title: CIP#15 - Add ETH/sETH pool
body:
To add a new ETH (wETH)/sETH pool.

This pool will allow a new money lego, with very efficient swap between all asset in [sUSD] – [sBTC] – [sETH] pools using Curve.fi and Synthetic/Kwenta exchange. Increasing fees for both protocols.
author: 0x052C60CEd52C7fD4Ac01FcCF0349CC495E3A2318
